license-file:        LICENSE
Homepage:            https://github.com/feuerbach/tasty-golden
Bug-reports:         https://github.com/feuerbach/tasty-golden/issues
author:              Roman Cheplyaka
maintainer:          Roman Cheplyaka <roma@ro-che.info>
